It's just a warning, and it's an easy fix. Just rename the boringssl repo in the tensorflow workspace, and the dependent rules accordingly. We jus haven't gotten around to it. PRs welcome.

An update to bazel may break the TensorFlow build, at which point we will be very motivated to fix this quickly.
